subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: David Chung, a junior at Stanford, survived an early run of birdies and eagles by Byeong-Hun An, the 2009 amateur champion, and rallied on the back nine for a 1-up victory in the semifinals of the 110th United States Amateur Championship.
